########## restart ##########

Syntax
  q = 'q'.

Verb q
  Does
    Quit.
End Verb.

Syntax
  'restart' = 'restart'.

Verb 'restart'
  Does
    Restart.
End Verb.

Syntax
  'score' = 'score'.

Verb 'score'
  Does
    Score .
End Verb.


The l1 Isa location
  
  Exit w To l2
    Does
      Score 5.
  End Exit.
  
End The l1.

The l2 Isa location
  
End The l2.

Start At l1.
  "Going w will give you 5 points. Then restart (or q) to find out if
   scores are cleared."
  
